# write-stories — WWA items

## When to invoke

The user wants backlog items in Why / What / Acceptance format.

## Steps

1. **Why** — strategic or user-centric reason this matters now.
2. **What** — crisp scope statement (includes / excludes).
3. **Acceptance** — testable conditions; prefer bullet list.
4. Keep items INVEST-friendly; split if too large.
5. Save where the team tracks backlog.
